#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigating Documents"
msgstr "Krmarjenje po dokumentih"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scrolling"
msgstr "Pomikanje"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You're probably familiar with the scrollbar that appears on the right side "
"(and sometimes the bottom) of documents, allowing you to move within "
"documents. However, there are several other ways you can navigate documents, "
"some of which are faster and easier."
msgstr ""
"Verjetno poznate drsni trak, ki se pojavi na desni strani (in včasih na dnu) "
"dokumentov in vam omogoča premikanje po dokumentih. Vendar pa obstaja več "
"drugih načinov za krmarjenje po dokumentih, od katerih so nekateri hitrejši "
"in lažji."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several mice have a wheel in the middle. You can move it up and down to "
"scroll within a document. If you press the &Shift; key while using the mouse "
"wheel, the document will scroll faster."
msgstr ""
"Več mišk ima kolo v sredini. Lahko ga premikate gor in dol, da se pomikate "
"po dokumentu. Če pritisnete &Shift; tipko medtem ko uporabljate kolešček "
"miške, se bo dokument premikal hitreje."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you're using a portable computer like a laptop, you might also be able to "
"scroll using the touchpad. Some computers allow you to scroll vertically by "
"moving your finger up and down the rightmost side of the touchpad, and allow "
"you to scroll horizontally by moving your finger across the bottommost side "
"of the touchpad. Others let you scroll using two fingers: move both fingers "
"up and down anywhere on the touchpad to scroll vertically, and move them "
"left and right to scroll horizontally. Since this functionality emulates the "
"mouse wheel functionality described above, you can also press the &Shift; "
"key while you do this to scroll faster."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate prenosni računalnik, kot je prenosnik, se boste morda lahko "
"pomikali tudi s sledilno ploščico. Nekateri računalniki vam omogočajo "
"navpično pomikanje s premikanjem prsta navzgor in navzdol po skrajni desni "
"strani sledilne ploščice in omogočajo vodoravno pomikanje s premikanjem "
"prsta po skrajni spodnji strani sledilne ploščice. Drugi vam omogočajo "
"drsenje z dvema prstoma: oba prsta premikajte navzgor in navzdol kamor koli "
"na sledilni ploščici, da se drsite navpično, ter ju premikajte levo in "
"desno, da se drsite vodoravno. Ker ta funkcija posnema zgoraj opisano "
"funkcijo kolesca miške, lahko pritisnete tudi &Shift; tipko, medtem ko to "
"počnete, da se pomikate hitreje."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use the &plasma-workspaces;, you can control mouse wheel behavior in "
"the <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/mouse/\">Mouse module in &systemsettings;</"
"ulink>, and you can control touchpad scrolling behavior in the Touchpad "
"module in &systemsettings;. Otherwise, look in the configuration area of "
"your operating system or desktop environment."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate &plasma-workspaces;, lahko nadzirate obnašanje miškinega "
"koleščka v <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/mouse/\">modulu miške v "
"&systemsettings;</ulink> in pomikanje sledilne ploščice v Modul sledilne "
"ploščice v &systemsettings;. V nasprotnem primeru poglejte v konfiguracijsko "
"območje vašega operacijskega sistema ali namiznega okolja."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, the scrollbar has several options in its context menu. You can "
"access these by right-clicking anywhere on the scrollbar. The following "
"options are available:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega ima drsni trak več možnosti v kontekstnem meniju. Do njih lahko "
"dostopate z desnim klikom kjer koli na drsnem traku. Na voljo so naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: tasks.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scroll here"
msgstr "Scroll here"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scroll directly to the location represented by where you right-clicked on "
"the scrollbar. This is the equivalent of simply clicking on that location on "
"the scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se neposredno do lokacije, ki jo predstavlja mesto, kjer ste z "
"desno miškino tipko kliknili drsni trak. To je enakovredno preprostemu kliku "
"na to mesto na drsnem traku."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Home</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Top</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Domov</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Na vrh</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the beginning of the document."
msgstr "Pojdi na začetek dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>End</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Bottom</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>Konec</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Dno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the end of the document."
msgstr "Pojdi na konec dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PgUp</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Page up</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PgUp</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Page up</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate to the previous page in a document that represents a printed "
"document, or one screen up in other types of documents."
msgstr ""
"Pomik na prejšnjo stran v dokumentu, ki predstavlja natisnjen dokument, ali "
"en zaslon navzgor v drugih vrstah dokumentov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PgDn</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Page down</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>PgDn</keycap></shortcut> <guimenuitem>Stran dol</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Navigate to the next page in a document that represents a printed document, "
"or one screen down in other types of documents."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se na naslednjo stran v dokumentu, ki predstavlja natisnjen "
"dokument, ali en zaslon navzdol v drugih vrstah dokumentov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scroll up"
msgstr "Pomakni navzgor"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scroll up one unit (usually a line) in the document. This is the equivalent "
"of clicking the up arrow at the top of the scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"Pomakni se navzgor za eno enoto (običajno vrstico) v dokumentu. To je "
"enakovredno kliku puščice navzgor na vrhu drsnega traku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scroll down"
msgstr "Pomakni navzdol"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Scroll down one unit (usually a line) in the document. This is the "
"equivalent of clicking the down arrow at the bottom of the scrollbar."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se navzdol za eno enoto (običajno vrstico) v dokumentu. To je "
"enakovredno kliku puščice navzdol na dnu drsnega traku."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zooming"
msgstr "Povečava"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many applications permit you to zoom. This makes the text or image you are "
"viewing larger or smaller. You can generally find the zoom function in the "
"<link linkend=\"menus-view\">View menu</link>, and sometimes in the status "
"bar of the application."
msgstr ""
"Številne aplikacije vam omogočajo povečavo. S tem se besedilo ali slika, ki "
"si jo ogledujete, poveča ali pomanjša. Funkcijo povečave običajno najdete v "
"<link linkend=\"menus-view\">meniju Pogled</link> in včasih v statusni "
"vrstici aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also zoom using the keyboard by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> to zoom in, or <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>-</keycap></keycombo> to zoom out. If you can scroll "
"with the mouse wheel or touchpad as described in <xref linkend=\"nav-scroll"
"\"/>, you can also zoom by pressing &Ctrl; and scrolling that way."
msgstr ""
"Povečate lahko tudi s tipkovnico tako, da pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>+</keycap></keycombo> za povečavo ali <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>- </keycap></keycombo> za pomanjšanje. Če se lahko "
"pomikate z miškinim kolescem ali sledilno ploščico, kot je opisano v <xref "
"linkend=\"nav-scroll\"/>, lahko povečate tudi s pritiskom &Ctrl; in "
"premikanje v tej smeri."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening and Saving Files"
msgstr "Odpiranje in shranjevanje datotek"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many &kde; applications work with files. Most applications have a "
"<guimenu>File</guimenu> menu with options that allow you to open and save "
"files. For more information on that, see <xref linkend=\"menus-file\"/>. "
"However, there are lots of different operations that require selecting a "
"file. Regardless of the method, all &kde; applications generally use the "
"same file selection window."
msgstr ""
"Veliko &kde; aplikacij dela z datotekami. Večina aplikacij ima meni "
"<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> z možnostmi, ki vam omogočajo odpiranje in "
"shranjevanje datotek. Za več informacij o tem glejte <xref linkend=\"menus-"
"file\"/>. Vendar obstaja veliko različnih operacij, ki zahtevajo izbiro "
"datoteke. Ne glede na metodo vse &kde; aplikacije običajno uporabljajo isto "
"okno za izbiro datotek."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Open Window"
msgstr "Okno za odpiranje datotek"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Open window."
msgstr "Okno za odpiranje datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opening a file in <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/internet/"
"konqueror/\">&konqueror;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Odpiranje datotek z <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/internet/"
"konqueror/\">&konqueror;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Selection Window"
msgstr "Okno za izbiro datotek"

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "This contains standard navigation tool buttons:"
msgstr "To vsebuje standardne gumbe orodij za krmarjenje:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the folder view to change to the previously displayed folder in its "
"history. This button is disabled, if there is no previous item."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči, da se pogled mape spremeni v prej prikazano mapo v njeni "
"zgodovini. Ta gumb je onemogočen, če ni prejšnjega elementa."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Naprej"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the folder view to change to the next folder in its history. This "
"button is disabled, if there is no next folder."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči, da se pogled mape spremeni v naslednjo mapo v njeni zgodovini. Ta "
"gumb je onemogočen, če ni naslednje mape."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Parent Folder"
msgstr "Nadrejena mapa"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will cause the folder view to change to the immediate parent of the "
"currently displayed folder, if possible."
msgstr ""
"To bo povzročilo, da se pogled mape spremeni v neposredni nadrejeni trenutno "
"prikazani mapi, če je to mogoče."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Reload</guibutton> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"
msgstr "<guibutton>Naloži znova</guibutton> (<keycap>F5</keycap>)"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:198
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Reloads the folder view, displaying any changes that have been made since it "
"was first loaded or last reloaded."
msgstr ""
"Ponovno naloži pogled mape in prikaže vse spremembe, ki so bile narejene od "
"prvega ali zadnjega ponovnega nalaganja."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Preview"
msgstr "Pokaži predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays a preview of each file inside the folder view."
msgstr "Prikaže predogled vsake datoteke znotraj mape."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:209
#, no-c-format
msgid "Zoom Slider"
msgstr "Drsnik za povečavo"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows you to change the size of the icon or preview shown in the "
"folder view."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča spreminjanje velikosti ikone ali predogleda, prikazanega v "
"pogledu mape."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guibutton>Options</guibutton>"
msgstr "<guibutton>Možnosti</guibutton>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>By "
"Name</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Po imenu</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort files listed in the folder view alphabetically by name."
msgstr "Razvrstite datoteke, navedene v pogledu mape, po abecedi imena."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>By "
"Size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Po velikosti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort files listed in the folder view in order of their file size."
msgstr "Datoteke, navedene v pogledu map, razvrstite po velikosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:245
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>By "
"Date</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Po datumu</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Sort files listed in the folder view by the date they were last modified."
msgstr ""
"Razvrstite datoteke, navedene v pogledu mape, po datumu, ko so bile nazadnje "
"spremenjene."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>By "
"Type</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Po vrsti</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort files listed in the folder view alphabetically by their file type."
msgstr ""
"Razvrstite datoteke, navedene v pogledu mape, po abecednem vrstnem redu "
"glede na tip datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Descending</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Padajoče</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When unchecked (the default), files in the folder view will be sorted in "
"ascending order. (For instance, files sorted alphabetically will be sorted "
"from A to Z, while files sorted numerically will be sorted from smallest to "
"largest.) When checked, files in the folder will be sorted in descending "
"order (in reverse)."
msgstr ""
"Če ni označeno (privzeto), bodo datoteke v pogledu mape razvrščene v "
"naraščajočem vrstnem redu. (Datoteke, razvrščene po abecedi, bodo na primer "
"razvrščene od A do Ž, medtem ko bodo datoteke razvrščene številčno, "
"razvrščene od najmanjše do največje.) Če je označeno, bodo datoteke v mapi "
"razvrščene v padajočem vrstnem redu (obratno)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>Sorting</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Folders First</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Razvrščanje</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Najprej mape</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:279
#, no-c-format
msgid "When enabled (the default), folders will appear before regular files."
msgstr ""
"Ko je omogočeno (privzeto), bodo mape prikazane pred običajnimi datotekami."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:295
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Short "
"View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Kratek pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays only the filenames."
msgstr "Prikaže samo imena datotek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Detailed View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Podroben pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:307
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays <guilabel>Name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Date</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Size</guilabel> of the files."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, <guilabel>Datum</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel> datotek."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Tree "
"View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Drevesni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Like Short View, but folders can be expanded to view their contents."
msgstr ""
"Kot Kratek pogled, vendar je mogoče mape razširiti za ogled njihove vsebine."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guisubmenu>View</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Detailed Tree View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Podroben drevesni pogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This also allows folders to be expanded, but displays the additional columns "
"available in Detailed View."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča tudi razširitev map, vendar prikaže dodatne stolpce, ki so na "
"voljo v podrobnem pogledu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Hidden Files</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži skrite datoteke</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays files or folders normally hidden by your operating system. The "
"alternate shortcut for this action is <keycap>F8</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže datoteke ali mape, ki jih vaš operacijski sistem običajno skrije. "
"Nadomestna bližnjica za to dejanje je <keycap>F8</keycap>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F9</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Options</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Places Navigation Panel</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycap>F9</keycap></shortcut> <guimenu>Možnosti</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži navigacijsko ploščo Mesta</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays the places panel which provides quick access to bookmarked "
"locations and disks or other media."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže ploščo mest, ki omogoča hiter dostop do označenih lokacij in diskov "
"ali drugih medijev."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:359
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Bookmarks</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži zaznamke</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays an additional icon on the toolbar that provides access to "
"<quote>bookmarks</quote>, a list of saved locations."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže dodatno ikono v orodni vrstici, ki omogoča dostop do "
"<quote>zaznamkov</quote>, seznama shranjenih lokacij."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: tasks.docbook:367
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Options</guimenu><guimenuitem>Show Aside Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Možnosti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži stranski predogled</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:370
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays a preview of the currently highlighted file to the right of the "
"folder view."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže predogled trenutno označene datoteke na desni strani pogleda mape."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: tasks.docbook:379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:380
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a submenu to edit or add bookmarks and to add a new bookmark folder."
msgstr ""
"Odpre podmeni za urejanje ali dodajanje zaznamkov in dodajanje nove mape z "
"zaznamki."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:390
#, no-c-format
msgid "Location Bar"
msgstr "Lokacijska vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The location bar, which can be found on top of the folder view, displays the "
"path to the current folder. The location bar has two modes:"
msgstr ""
"Lokacijska vrstica, ki jo najdete na vrhu pogleda mape, prikazuje pot do "
"trenutne mape. Lokacijska vrstica ima dva načina:"

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:397
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bread Crumb Mode"
msgstr "Način kruhovih drobtin"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <quote>bread crumb</quote> mode, which is the default, each folder "
"name in the path to the current folder is a button which can be clicked to "
"quickly open that folder. Moreover, clicking the <quote>&gt;</quote> sign to "
"the right of a folder opens a menu which permits to quickly open a subfolder "
"of that folder."
msgstr ""
"V načinu <quote>drobtin kruha</quote>, ki je privzet, je vsako ime mape na "
"poti do trenutne mape gumb, ki ga lahko kliknete za hitro odpiranje te mape. "
"Poleg tega se s klikom na znak <quote>&gt;</quote> na desni strani mape "
"odpre meni, ki omogoča hitro odpiranje podmape te mape."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in bread crumb mode"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona lokacijske vrstice v načinu kruhovih drobtin"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:412
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu kruhovih drobtin.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in bread crumb mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu kruhovih drobtin.</para>"

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editable Mode"
msgstr "Način za urejanje"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When in bread crumb mode, clicking in the gray area to the right of the path "
"with the &LMB; switches the location bar to the <quote>editable</quote> "
"mode, in which the path can be edited using the keyboard. To switch back to "
"bread crumb mode, click the check mark at the right of the location bar with "
"the &LMB;."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste v načinu kruhovih drobtin, kliknite v sivo območje desno od poti z "
"&LMB; preklopi lokacijsko vrstico v način <quote>urejanja</quote>, v katerem "
"je mogoče pot urejati s tipkovnico. Če želite preklopiti nazaj v način "
"kruhovih drobtin, z &LMB; kliknite kljukico na desni strani lokacijske "
"vrstice."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:431
#, no-c-format
msgid "Screenshot of the location bar in editable mode"
msgstr "Posnetek zaslona lokacijske vrstice v načinu za urejanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:437
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar in editable mode.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu za urejanje.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:439
#, no-c-format
msgid "<para>Location bar in editable mode.</para>"
msgstr "<para>Lokacijska vrstica v načinu za urejanje.</para>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu of the location bar offers action to switch between the "
"modes and to copy and paste the path using the clipboard. Check the last "
"option in this context menu to display either the full path starting with "
"the root folder of the file system or to display the path starting with the "
"current places entry."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstni meni lokacijske vrstice ponuja dejanje za preklapljanje med "
"načini ter kopiranje in lepljenje poti z uporabo odložišča. Označite zadnjo "
"možnost v tem kontekstnem meniju, če želite prikazati bodisi celotno pot, ki "
"se začne s korensko mapo datotečnega sistema, bodisi prikazati pot, ki se "
"začne z vnosom trenutnih mest."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Location bar context menu</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Kontekstni meni lokacijske vrstice</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Location bar context menu</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Kontekstni meni lokacijske vrstice</phrase>"

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Places</guilabel> List"
msgstr "Seznam <guilabel>mest</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:497
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This provides the standard &kde; list of Places, shared with &dolphin; and "
"other file management tools."
msgstr ""
"To zagotavlja standardni &kde; seznam mest, ki je v skupni rabi z &dolphin; "
"in drugimi orodji za upravljanje datotek."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:508
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Folder View"
msgstr "Pogled mape"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:510
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The largest part of the file selection window is the area that lists all "
"items in the current directory. To select a file, you can double-click on "
"it, or choose one and hit <guibutton>Open</guibutton> or <guibutton>Save</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Največji del okna za izbiro datoteke je območje, ki navaja vse elemente v "
"trenutnem imeniku. Datoteko izberete tako, da dvokliknete nanjo ali jo "
"izberete in pritisnete <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Shrani</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:515
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select multiple files at once. To select specific files, or to "
"unselect specific files that are already selected, press and hold &Ctrl;, "
"click on each file, then release &Ctrl;. To select a contiguous group of "
"files, click the first file, press and hold &Shift;, click on the last file "
"in the group, and release &Shift;."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko tudi več datotek hkrati. Če želite izbrati določene datoteke "
"ali preklicati izbor določenih datotek, ki so že izbrane, pritisnite in "
"držite &Ctrl;, kliknite posamezno datoteko in nato spustite &Ctrl;. Če "
"želite izbrati sosednjo skupino datotek, kliknite prvo datoteko, pritisnite "
"in držite &Shift;, kliknite zadnjo datoteko v skupini in spustite &Shift;."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Folder View supports a limited set of file operations, which can be "
"accessed by right-clicking on a file to access its context menu, or using "
"keyboard shortcuts. The following items are available in the context menu:"
msgstr ""
"Pogled mape podpira omejen nabor operacij z datotekami, do katerih lahko "
"dostopate z desnim klikom na datoteko za dostop do njenega kontekstnega "
"menija ali z uporabo bližnjic na tipkovnici. V kontekstnem meniju so na "
"voljo naslednji elementi:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: tasks.docbook:528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create New..."
msgstr "Ustvari novo..."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a new file or folder."
msgstr "Ustvari novo datoteko ali mapo."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Move to Trash...</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Premakni v koš ...</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul"
"\"><keycap>Del</keycap></keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:535
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the currently selected item to the trash."
msgstr "Premakni trenutno izbrani element v koš."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: tasks.docbook:539
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sorting"
msgstr "Razvrščanje"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:540
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu can also be accessed from the toolbar, and is described in "
"<xref linkend=\"files-ui-toolbar-options-sorting\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Do tega podmenija lahko dostopate tudi iz orodne vrstice in je opisan v "
"<xref linkend=\"files-ui-toolbar-options-sorting\"/>."

#. Tag: guisubmenu
#: tasks.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "View"
msgstr "Ogled"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This submenu can also be accessed from the toolbar, and is described in "
"<xref linkend=\"files-ui-toolbar-options-view\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Do tega podmenija lahko dostopate tudi iz orodne vrstice in je opisan v "
"<xref linkend=\"files-ui-toolbar-options-view\"/>."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: tasks.docbook:551
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open File Manager"
msgstr "Odprite upravitelja datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:552
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the current folder in your default file manager application."
msgstr "Odpre trenutno mapo v vaši privzeti aplikaciji za upravljanje datotek."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenuitem>Properties</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;"
"&Enter;</keycombo>)"
msgstr ""
"<guimenuitem>Lastnosti</guimenuitem> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Enter;"
"</keycombo>)"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the Properties window that allows you to view and modify various types "
"of metadata related to the currently selected file."
msgstr ""
"Odprite okno Lastnosti, ki vam omogoča ogled in spreminjanje različnih vrst "
"metapodatkov, povezanih s trenutno izbrano datoteko."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:568
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Preview Pane"
msgstr "Podokno za predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid "If enabled, this displays a preview of the currently highlighted file."
msgstr "Če je omogočeno, prikaže predogled trenutno označene datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:574
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Name</guilabel> Entry"
msgstr "Vnos <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a file is selected, a name will appear in this text box. You may also "
"manually enter a file name or path in this text box."
msgstr ""
"Ko je datoteka izbrana, se bo v tem besedilnem polju pojavilo ime. V to "
"besedilno polje lahko tudi ročno vnesete ime datoteke ali pot do nje."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> Entry"
msgstr "Vnos <guilabel>Filter</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When opening a file, the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> entry allows you to "
"enter a filter for the files displayed in the folder view. The filter uses "
"standard globs; patterns must be separated by white space. For instance, you "
"can enter <userinput>*.cpp *.h *.moc</userinput> to display several "
"different common &Qt; programming files."
msgstr ""
"Ko odprete datoteko, vam vnos <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> omogoča vnos "
"filtra za datoteke, prikazane v pogledu mape. Filter uporablja standardne "
"globs; vzorci morajo biti ločeni s presledkom. Vnesete lahko na primer "
"<userinput>*.cpp *.h *.moc</userinput> za prikaz več različnih pogostih &Qt; "
"programskih datotek."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display all files, enter a single asterisk (<userinput>*</userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz vseh datotek vnesite eno zvezdico (<userinput>*</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:591
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter entry saves the last 10 filters entered between sessions. To use "
"one, press the arrow button on the right of the entry and select the desired "
"filter string. You can disable the filter by pressing the <guibutton>Clear "
"text</guibutton> button to the left of the autocompletion arrow button."
msgstr ""
"Vnos filtra shrani zadnjih 10 filtrov, vnesenih med sejami. Če ga želite "
"uporabiti, pritisnite puščični gumb na desni strani vnosa in izberite želeni "
"niz filtrov. Filter lahko onemogočite tako, da pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Počisti besedilo</guibutton> levo od puščičnega gumba za "
"samodokončanje."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:597
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When saving a file, the <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> entry will instead "
"display a drop down box that allows you to select from all the file types "
"the application supports. Select one to save a file in that format."
msgstr ""
"Ko shranjujete datoteko, bo vnos <guilabel>Filter</guilabel> namesto tega "
"prikazal spustno polje, ki vam omogoča izbiro med vsemi vrstami datotek, ki "
"jih podpira aplikacija. Izberite eno, da shranite datoteko v tej obliki."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically select filename extension"
msgstr "Samodejno izberi končnico imena datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:605
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When saving a file, this check box will appear. When selected (the default), "
"the application will automatically append the default file extension for the "
"selected file type to the end of the file name, if it does not already "
"appear in the <guilabel>Name</guilabel> entry. The file extension that will "
"be used is listed in parenthesis at the end of the check box label."
msgstr ""
"Ko shranjujete datoteko, se prikaže to potrditveno polje. Ko je izbrana "
"(privzeto), bo aplikacija samodejno dodala privzeto pripono datoteke za "
"izbrano vrsto datoteke na konec imena datoteke, če še ni prikazana v vnosu "
"<guilabel>Ime</guilabel>. Pripona datoteke, ki bo uporabljena, je navedena v "
"oklepaju na koncu oznake potrditvenega polja."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:613
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Save Window"
msgstr "Okno za shranjevanje datoteke"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:616
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Save window."
msgstr "Okno za shranjevanje datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Saving a file in <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/internet/"
"konqueror/\">&konqueror;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Shranjevanje datoteke v <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/applications/"
"internet/konqueror/\">&konqueror;</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:627
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guibutton>Open</guibutton> or <guibutton>Save</guibutton> Button"
msgstr "Gumb <guibutton>Odpri</guibutton> ali <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Depending on the action being performed, an <guibutton>Open</guibutton> or "
"<guibutton>Save</guibutton> button will be displayed. Clicking on this "
"button will close the file selection window and perform the requested action."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od dejanja, ki se izvaja, bo prikazan gumb <guibutton>Odpri</"
"guibutton> ali <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>. S klikom na ta gumb se zapre "
"okno za izbiro datoteke in izvede zahtevano dejanje."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> Button"
msgstr "Gumb <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> will close the file dialog without "
"performing any action."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, boste zaprli pogovorno okno "
"datoteke, ne da bi izvedli kakršno koli dejanje."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:645 tasks.docbook:763 tasks.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thanks and Acknowledgments"
msgstr "Hvala in zahvala"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 participant Alexey Subach for writing "
"parts of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 Alexeyu Subachu za pisanje "
"delov tega razdelka."

#. Tag: author
#: tasks.docbook:658
#, no-c-format
msgid "&David.Sweet; &David.Sweet.mail;"
msgstr "&David.Sweet; &David.Sweet.mail;"

#. Tag: author
#: tasks.docbook:659
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Salma</firstname> <surname>Sultana</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>Salma</firstname> <surname>Sultana</surname>"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:664 tasks.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check Spelling"
msgstr "Preveri črkovanje"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:666
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sonnet; is the spelling checker used by &kde; applications such as &kate;, "
"&kmail;, and &calligrawords;. It is a &GUI; frontend to various free spell "
"checkers."
msgstr ""
"&sonnet; je črkovalnik, ki ga uporabljajo &kde; aplikacije, kot so &kate;, "
"&kmail; in &calligrawords;. Je &GUI; vmesnik za različne brezplačne "
"črkovalnike."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:669
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use &sonnet; you need to install a spell checker like <application>&GNU; "
"Aspell</application>, <application>Hspell</application> or "
"<application>Hunspell</application> and additionally the corresponding "
"dictionaries for the languages that you wish to use."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo &sonnet; morate namestiti črkovalnik, kot je <application>&GNU; "
"Aspell</application>, <application>Hspell</application> ali "
"<application>Hunspell</application> in dodatno ustrezne slovarje za jezike, "
"ki želite uporabiti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Check Spelling Window"
msgstr "Okno za preverjanje črkovanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Check spelling window."
msgstr "Okno za preverjanje črkovanja."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correcting a misspelling."
msgstr "Popravljanje napake pri črkovanju."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To check spelling, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite preveriti črkovanje, pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Črkovanje ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a word is possibly misspelled in your document, it is displayed in the "
"top line in the dialog. &sonnet; tries to appropriate word(s) for "
"replacement. The best guess is displayed to the right of <guilabel>Replace "
"with</guilabel>. To accept this replacement, click on <guibutton>Replace</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če je beseda v vašem dokumentu morda napačno črkovana, je prikazana v "
"zgornji vrstici pogovornega okna. &sonnet; poskuša prisvojiti besedo(e) za "
"zamenjavo. Najboljše ugibanje je prikazano desno od <guilabel>Zamenjaj z</"
"guilabel>. Če želite sprejeti to zamenjavo, kliknite <guibutton>Zamenjaj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sonnet; also allows you to select a word from the list of suggestions and "
"replace the misspelled word with that selected word. With the help of the "
"<guibutton>Suggest</guibutton> button, you can add more suggestions from the "
"dictionary to the suggestions list."
msgstr ""
"&sonnet; omogoča tudi izbiro besede s seznama predlogov in zamenjavo napačno "
"črkovane besede s to izbrano besedo. S pomočjo gumba <guibutton>Predlagaj</"
"guibutton> lahko dodate več predlogov iz slovarja na seznam predlogov."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on <guibutton>Ignore</guibutton> to keep your original spelling."
msgstr "Kliknite <guibutton>Prezri</guibutton>, da ohranite prvotno črkovanje."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Finished</guibutton> to stop spellchecking and "
"<emphasis>keep</emphasis> the changes made."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Končano</guibutton>, da ustavite preverjanje črkovanja "
"in <emphasis>obdržite</emphasis> narejene spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to stop spellchecking and "
"<emphasis>cancel</emphasis> the changes already made."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Prekliči</guibutton>, da ustavite preverjanje črkovanja "
"in <emphasis>prekličete</emphasis> že narejene spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> to automatically replace the "
"misspelled word(s) with the chosen replacement word, if they appear again in "
"your document later."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Zamenjaj vse</guibutton>, da samodejno zamenjate napačno "
"črkovane besede z izbrano nadomestno besedo, če se pozneje znova pojavijo v "
"vašem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Ignore All</guibutton> to ignore the spelling at that "
"point and all the future occurrences of the word misspelled."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Prezri vse</guibutton>, da prezrete črkovanje na tej "
"točki in za vse prihodnje pojavitve napačno črkovane besede."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Add to Dictionary</guibutton> to add the misspelled word "
"to your personal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guibutton>Dodaj v slovar</guibutton>, da dodate napačno črkovano "
"besedo v svoj osebni slovar."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Personal Dictionary</guilabel> is a distinct dictionary from "
"the system dictionary and the additions made by you will not be seen by "
"others."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Osebni slovar</guilabel> je slovar, ki se razlikuje od sistemskega "
"slovarja. Drugi ne bodo videli vaših dodatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The drop down box <guilabel>Language</guilabel> at the bottom of this dialog "
"allows you to switch to another dictionary temporarily."
msgstr ""
"Spustno polje <guilabel>Jezik</guilabel> na dnu tega pogovornega okna vam "
"omogoča začasen preklop na drug slovar."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Spell Checking"
msgstr "Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In many applications, you can automatically check spelling as you type. To "
"enable this feature, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"V številnih aplikacijah lahko samodejno preverjate črkovanje med tipkanjem. "
"Če želite omogočiti to funkcijo, izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Samodejno preverjanje črkovanja</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Potentially misspelled words will be underlined in red. To select a "
"suggestion, right click on the word, select the <guisubmenu>Spelling</"
"guisubmenu> submenu, and select the suggestion. You may also instruct "
"&sonnet; to ignore this spelling for this document by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Ignore Word</guimenuitem>, or you may select <guimenuitem>Add "
"to Dictionary</guimenuitem> to save it in your personal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Morebitne napačno črkovane besede bodo podčrtane z rdečo. Če želite izbrati "
"predlog, z desno miškino tipko kliknite besedo, izberite podmeni "
"<guisubmenu>Črkovanje</guisubmenu> in izberite predlog. Lahko tudi naročite "
"&sonnet; če želite prezreti to črkovanje za ta dokument, tako da izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Prezri besedo</guimenuitem> ali pa izberete <guimenuitem>Dodaj "
"v slovar</guimenuitem>, da ga shranite v svoj osebni slovar."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &sonnet;"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje &sonnet;"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change your dictionary, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A small window "
"will appear at the bottom of the current document that will allow you to "
"change your dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti svoj slovar, pojdite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Spremeni slovar ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Na dnu "
"trenutnega dokumenta se prikaže majhno okno, v katerem lahko spremenite svoj "
"slovar."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on configuring &sonnet;, see the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/spellchecking\">Spell Checker &systemsettings; module "
"documentation</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o konfiguraciji &sonnet; glejte <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/spellchecking\">Črkovalnik &systemsettings; dokumentacija modula</"
"ulink>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 Participant Salma Sultana for writing "
"much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeleženki Google Code-In 2011 Salmi Sultani za pisanje "
"večjega dela tega razdelka."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find and Replace"
msgstr "Poišči in zamenjaj"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find function of many &kde; applications lets you find specific text in "
"a document, while the Replace function allows you to replace text that is "
"found with different text you provide."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija Poišči mnogih &kde; aplikacij vam omogoča iskanje določenega "
"besedila v dokumentu, medtem ko vam funkcija Zamenjaj omogoča zamenjavo "
"najdenega besedila z drugim besedilom, ki ga vnesete."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find both these functions in the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu of "
"many &kde; applications. For more information on this menu, see <xref "
"linkend=\"menus-edit\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Obe funkciji najdete v meniju <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> mnogih &kde; "
"aplikacij. Za več informacij o tem meniju glejte <xref linkend=\"menus-edit"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find Function"
msgstr "Funkcija poišči"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find function searches for text in a document and selects it."
msgstr "Funkcija poišči v dokumentu išče neko besedilo in ga označi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find Window"
msgstr "Okno za iskanje"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find window."
msgstr "Okno za iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Searching for <userinput>income</userinput> in <ulink url=\"https://www.kde."
"org/applications/office/sheets/\">&calligrasheets;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje <userinput>income</userinput> v <ulink url=\"https://www.kde.org/"
"applications/office/sheets/\">&calligrasheets;</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use Find in many applications, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or press <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Then, in the <guilabel>Text "
"to find:</guilabel> text box, enter the text that you want to find."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabiti Iskanje v številnih aplikacijah, pojdite na "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Najdi ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> ali pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap> F</"
"keycap></keycombo>. Nato v besedilno polje <guilabel>Besedilo za iskanje:</"
"guilabel> vnesite besedilo, ki ga želite najti."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Regular expression</guilabel> is checked you will be able to "
"search using regular expressions. Click on <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> to "
"select from and enter commonly used regular expression characters, like "
"<guilabel>White Space</guilabel> or <guilabel>Start of Line</guilabel>. If "
"&kate; is installed, you can find <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-"
"expressions.html\">more information on writing regular expressions in its "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če je označen <guilabel>Regularni izraz</guilabel>, boste lahko iskali z "
"regularnimi izrazi. Kliknite <guibutton>Uredi</guibutton>, da izberete in "
"vnesete pogosto uporabljene znake regularnih izrazov, kot je "
"<guilabel>Presledek</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Začetek vrstice</guilabel>. Če "
"&kate; nameščen, lahko najdete <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-"
"expressions.html\">več informacij o pisanju regularnih izrazov v njegovi "
"dokumentaciji</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can limit the found results by configuring these options:"
msgstr "You can limit the found results by configuring these options:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Razlikuje med velikimi in malimi črkami"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital and lowercase characters are considered different. For example, if "
"you search for <quote>This</quote>, results that contain <quote>this</quote> "
"will not be returned."
msgstr ""
"Velike in male črke se štejejo za različne. Če na primer iščete <quote>To</"
"quote>, rezultati, ki vsebujejo <quote>to</quote>, ne bodo vrnjeni."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whole words only"
msgstr "Samo cele besede"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, when the application searches for text, it will return results "
"even in the middle of other text. For instance, if you search for <quote>is</"
"quote> it will stop on every word that contains that, like "
"<quote>th<emphasis>is</emphasis></quote> or <quote>h<emphasis>is</"
"emphasis>tory</quote>. If you check this option, the application will only "
"return results when the search text is a word by itself, that is, surrounded "
"by whitespace."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto bo aplikacija, ko išče besedilo, vrnila rezultate tudi sredi "
"drugega besedila. Če na primer iščete <quote>to</quote>, se bo ustavilo na "
"vsaki besedi, ki to vsebuje, na primer <quote>av<emphasis>to</emphasis></"
"quote> ali <quote>kalkula<emphasis> to</emphasis>r</quote>. Če označite to "
"možnost, bo aplikacija vrnila rezultate samo, če je iskalno besedilo beseda "
"sama po sebi, torej obdana s presledkom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "From cursor"
msgstr "Od miškinega kazalca"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search will start from the location of the cursor and stop at the end of "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje se bo začelo od lokacije kazalca in ustavilo na koncu besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find backwards"
msgstr "Poišči nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the application searches for the text starting at the beginning "
"of the document, and move through it to the end. If you check this option, "
"it will instead start at the end and work its way to the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto aplikacija išče besedilo, ki se začne na začetku dokumenta, in se "
"premika po njem do konca. Če označite to možnost, se bo namesto tega začelo "
"iskanje na koncu in nadaljevalo pot do začetka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected text"
msgstr "Izbrano besedilo"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to search only in the text that is currently selected, "
"not the entire document. It is disabled when no text is selected."
msgstr ""
"Izberite to možnost, če želite iskati samo po besedilu, ki je trenutno "
"izbrano, ne po celotnem dokumentu. Ko besedilo ni izbrano, je onemogočena."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:875
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many applications show a search bar instead of the Find window. See <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace.html#finding-text\">&katepart; "
"documentation</ulink> for additional information on the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Številne aplikacije namesto okna Poišči prikažejo iskalno vrstico. Glejte "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace.html#finding-text"
"\">&katepart; dokumentacijo</ulink> za dodatne informacije v iskalni vrstici."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The search bar in &kate;.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Iskalna vrstica v &kate;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The search bar in &kate;.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Iskalna vrstica v &kate;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching for <userinput>software</userinput> in &kate;'s search bar."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje <userinput>programja</userinput> v iskalni vrstici programa &kate;."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find function only selects the first match that it finds. You can "
"continue searching by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or by pressing "
"<keycap>F3</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija Najdi izbere samo prvo ujemanje, ki ga najde. Iskanje lahko "
"nadaljujete tako, da izberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Poišči naslednje</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ali "
"pritisnete <keycap>F3</keycap>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example of a Search"
msgstr "Primer iskanja"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example of a search."
msgstr "Primer iskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:898
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; displays a match for <userinput>KDE</userinput>."
msgstr "kate; prikaže ujemanje za <userinput>KDE</userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace Function"
msgstr "Funkcija Zamenjaj"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Replace function searches for text in a document and replaces it with "
"other text. You can find it in many application at "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Replace...</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> or by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija Zamenjaj poišče besedilo v dokumentu in ga nadomesti z drugim "
"besedilom. Najdete ga v številnih aplikacijah na <menuchoice><guimenu>Uredi</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Zamenjaj ...</guisubmenu></menuchoice> ali s pritiskom "
"na <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap> R</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace Window"
msgstr "Okno zamenjaj"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace window."
msgstr "Okno zamenjaj."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:919
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replacing <userinput>income</userinput> with <userinput>expense</userinput> "
"in &calligrasheets;"
msgstr ""
"Zamenjava <userinput>dohodka</userinput> z <userinput>odhodkom</userinput> v "
"&calligrasheets;"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid "The window of the Replace function is separated into 3 sections:"
msgstr "Okno funkcije Zamenjaj je razdeljeno na 3 dele:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Poišči"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may enter the text you wish to search for. See <xref linkend=\"find-"
"find\"/> for more information on the options provided here."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete besedilo, ki ga želite iskati. Glejte <xref linkend="
"\"find-find\"/> za več informacij o možnostih, ki so na voljo tukaj."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Zamenjaj"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you may enter the text you wish to replace the found text with."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko vnesete besedilo, s katerim želite zamenjati najdeno besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reuse the found text in the replacement text by selecting the "
"<guilabel>Use placeholders</guilabel> checkbox. Placeholders, sometimes "
"known as backreferences, are a special character sequence that will be "
"replaced with all or part of the found text. For instance, <quote>\\0</"
"quote> represents the entire found string."
msgstr ""
"Najdeno besedilo lahko ponovno uporabite v nadomestnem besedilu, tako da "
"izberete potrditveno polje <guilabel>Uporabi nadomestne oznake</guilabel>. "
"Oznake mesta, včasih znane kot povratne reference, so posebno zaporedje "
"znakov, ki bo nadomeščeno z vsem ali delom najdenega besedila. Na primer, "
"<quote>\\0</quote> predstavlja celoten najdeni niz."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may insert placeholders into the text box by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Insert Placeholder</guibutton> button, then selecting an option "
"from the menu like <guimenuitem>Complete Match</guimenuitem>. For example, "
"if you are searching for <quote>message</quote>, and you want to replace it "
"with <guilabel>messages</guilabel> insert the <guimenuitem>Complete Match</"
"guimenuitem> placeholder and add an <quote>s</quote>. The replace field will "
"then contain <quote>\\0s</quote>."
msgstr ""
"V besedilno polje lahko vstavite nadomestne oznake tako, da kliknete gumb "
"<guibutton>Vstavi nadomestni znak</guibutton> in nato izberete možnost v "
"meniju, kot je <guimenuitem>Popolno ujemanje</guimenuitem>. Na primer, če "
"iščete <quote>sporočilo</quote> in ga želite zamenjati z "
"<guilabel>sporočila</guilabel>, vstavite nadomestno oznako "
"<guimenuitem>Popolno ujemanje</guimenuitem> in dodajte <quote> s</quote>. "
"Polje za zamenjavo bo nato vsebovalo <quote>\\0s</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kate; is installed, you can learn more about placeholders in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\">Regular Expressions appendix "
"of its documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če je &kate; nameščen, lahko izveste več o nadomestnih oznakah v <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\"> Regularni izrazi dodatku "
"dokumentacije</ulink> &kate;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Options</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Možnosti</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This contains all the same options that the <link linkend=\"find-find"
"\">Find</link> function does, with one addition:"
msgstr ""
"To vsebuje vse enake možnosti kot funkcija <link linkend=\"find-find"
"\">Poišči</link>, z enim dodatkom:"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Prompt on replace</guilabel> option is checked a window "
"will appear on every found word, allowing you to confirm whether you would "
"like to replace the found text."
msgstr ""
"Če je možnost <guilabel>Poziv ob zamenjavi</guilabel> označena, se bo ob "
"vsaki najdeni besedi pojavilo okno, v katerem lahko potrdite, ali želite "
"zamenjati najdeno besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:972
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many Applications show a search and replace bar instead of the Replace "
"window. See <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace."
"html#replacing-text\">&katepart; documentation</ulink> for additional "
"information on the search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Številne aplikacije namesto okna Zamenjaj prikažejo vrstico za iskanje in "
"zamenjavo. Glejte <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace."
"html#replacing-text\">&katepart; dokumentacijo</ulink> za dodatne "
"informacije o vrstici za iskanje in zamenjavo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The search and replace bar.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Vrstica za iskanje in zamenjavo.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The search and replace bar.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Vrstica za iskanje in zamenjavo.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replacing <userinput>kmail</userinput> with <userinput>kate</userinput> in "
"&kate;'s search and replace bar"
msgstr ""
"Zamenjava <userinput>kmail</userinput> z <userinput>kate</userinput> v "
"&kate; v vrstici za iskanje in zamenjavo"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thanks to an anonymous Google Code-In 2011 participant for writing much of "
"this section."
msgstr ""
"Hvala anonimnemu udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 za pisanje večjega dela tega "
"razdelka."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing Fonts"
msgstr "Izbiranje pisav"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The font selector appears in many different &kde; applications. It lets you "
"select the font face, font style, and font size of the text that appears in "
"your application."
msgstr ""
"Izbirnik pisave se pojavi v številnih različnih &kde; aplikacije. Omogoča "
"vam izbiro pisave, sloga pisave in velikosti pisave besedila, ki se pojavi v "
"vaši aplikaciji."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Font Selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik pisave"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "The font selector."
msgstr "Izbirnik pisave."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting a font in <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Izbira pisave v <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font"
msgstr "Pisava"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the leftmost selection box, and lets you choose the font face from a "
"list of fonts on your system."
msgstr ""
"To je skrajno levo izbirno polje in vam omogoča izbiro pisave s seznama "
"pisav v vašem sistemu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font style"
msgstr "Slog pisave"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the center selection box, and lets you choose the font style from "
"the following choices:"
msgstr ""
"To je sredinsko izbirno polje in omogoča izbiro sloga pisave med naslednjimi "
"možnostmi:"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Italic</guilabel> - this displays text in a cursive, or slanted "
"fashion, and is commonly used for citations or to emphasize text."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Ležeče</guilabel> - to prikaže besedilo v kurzivu ali poševno in "
"se običajno uporablja za navedbe ali poudarjanje besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Regular</guilabel> - the default. Text is displayed without any "
"special appearance."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Običajno</guilabel> - privzeto. Besedilo je prikazano brez "
"posebnega videza."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bold Italic</guilabel> - a combination of both <guilabel>Bold</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Italic</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Krepko ležeče</guilabel> – kombinacija obeh <guilabel>Krepko</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Ležeče</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bold</guilabel> - this displays text in a darker, thicker fashion, "
"and is commonly used for titles of documents or to emphasize text."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Krepko</guilabel> - to prikaže besedilo na temnejši in debelejši "
"način in se običajno uporablja za naslove dokumentov ali za poudarjanje "
"besedila."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size"
msgstr "Velikost"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1056
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the rightmost selection box, and lets you select the size of your "
"text. Font size is measured in <emphasis>points</emphasis>, a standard unit "
"of measure in typography. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_(typography)\">the <quote>Point "
"(typography)</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"To je skrajno desno izbirno polje in omogoča izbiro velikosti besedila. "
"Velikost pisave se meri v <emphasis>točkah</emphasis>, kar je standardna "
"merska enota v tipografiji. Za več informacij o tem glejte <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_(typography)\">članek <quote>Point "
"(tipografija)</quote> na Wikipediji</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Predogled"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom of the font selector displays a preview of text using the font "
"settings that are currently selected. You may change this text if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu izbirnika pisave je prikazan predogled besedila z uporabo nastavitev "
"pisave, ki so trenutno izbrane. To besedilo lahko, če želite, spremenite."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing Colors"
msgstr "Izbiranje barv"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color chooser appears in many &kde; applications, whenever you need to "
"select a color. It lets you pick from a <guilabel>Basic colors</guilabel> "
"consisting of many predefined colors or mix your own when you want a "
"specific color."
msgstr ""
"Izbirnik barv se pojavi v mnogih &kde; aplikacijah, kadarkoli morate izbrati "
"barvo. Omogoča vam, da izbirate med <guilabel>Osnovnimi barvami</guilabel>, "
"ki so sestavljene iz številnih vnaprej določenih barv, ali zmešate svojo, ko "
"želite določeno barvo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Color Selector"
msgstr "Izbirnik barve"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "The color selector."
msgstr "Izbirnik barve."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting a color in <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Izbira barve na <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Basic Colors"
msgstr "Uporaba osnovnih barv"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The basic colors group is a set of predefined colors. You can find it on the "
"top side of the color chooser window."
msgstr ""
"Skupina osnovnih barv je nabor vnaprej določenih barv. Najdete jih na "
"zgornji strani okna za izbiro barv."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a color from the basic colors, simply click on it. The color will "
"be displayed at the right of the palette, along with its &HTML; hexadecimal "
"code"
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati barvo izmed osnovnih barv, preprosto kliknite nanjo. Barva "
"bo prikazana na desni strani palete, skupaj z &HTML; šestnajstiško kodo"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mixing Colors"
msgstr "Mešanje barv"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color chooser also lets you mix your own colors. There are several ways "
"to do this:"
msgstr ""
"Izbirnik barv vam omogoča tudi mešanje lastnih barv. To lahko storite na več "
"načinov:"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Grid"
msgstr "Uporaba mreže"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The right side of the color chooser contains a large box, and a thinner box "
"immediately to its right. You can use the left box to select the Hue and "
"Saturation of the desired color based on the visual guide provided in the "
"box. The right bar adjusts the Value. Adjust these to select the desired "
"color, which is displayed in the middle of the window."
msgstr ""
"Desna stran izbirnika barv vsebuje veliko polje in tanjše polje takoj desno. "
"Levo polje lahko uporabite za izbiro odtenka in nasičenosti želene barve na "
"podlagi vizualnega vodnika v polju. Desna vrstica prilagodi vrednost. "
"Prilagodite jih, da izberete želeno barvo, ki bo prikazana na sredini okna."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on Hue, Saturation, and Value, see <xref linkend="
"\"colors-mixing-hsv\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o barvnem odtenku, nasičenosti in vrednosti glejte <xref "
"linkend=\"colors-mixing-hsv\"/>"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Screen Colors"
msgstr "Uporaba barv zaslona"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eyedropper tool allows you to select a color from your screen. To use "
"it, select the <guibutton>Pick Screen Color</guibutton> button below the "
"basic colors, and then click anywhere on your screen to select that color."
msgstr ""
"Orodje za kapalko vam omogoča izbiro barve na zaslonu. Če ga želite "
"uporabiti, izberite gumb <guibutton>Izberi barvo zaslona</guibutton> pod "
"osnovnimi barvami in nato kliknite kjerkoli na zaslonu, da izberete to barvo."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hue/Saturation/Value"
msgstr "Odtenek/nasičenost/vrednost"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower-right corner of the screen allows you to manually enter the "
"coordinates of the desired color in the Hue/Saturation/Value (<acronym>HSV</"
"acronym>) color space. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HSL_and_HSV\">the <quote>HSL and HSV</quote> "
"article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"V spodnjem desnem kotu zaslona lahko ročno vnesete koordinate želene barve v "
"barvni prostor Odtenek/nasičenost/vrednost (<acronym>ONV</acronym>). Za več "
"informacij o tem glejte <ulink url=\"https://hmn.wiki/sl/HSV_color_space"
"\">članek <quote>HSL in HSV</quote></ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1147 tasks.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These values are also updated when selecting a color by other methods, so "
"they always accurately represent the currently selected color."
msgstr ""
"Te vrednosti se posodobijo tudi pri izbiri barve z drugimi metodami, tako da "
"vedno natančno predstavljajo trenutno izbrano barvo."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Red/Green/Blue"
msgstr "Rdeča/Zelena/Modra"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower-right corner of the screen also allows you to manually enter the "
"coordinates of the desired color in the Red/Green/Blue (<acronym>RGB</"
"acronym>) color model. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RGB_color_model\">the <quote>RGB color "
"model</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Spodnji desni kot zaslona omogoča tudi ročni vnos koordinat želene barve v "
"barvnem modelu rdeča/zelena/modra (<acronym>RGB</acronym>). Za več "
"informacij o tem glejte <ulink url=\"https://sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/"
"Barvni_model_RGB\">članek o <quote>barvnem modelu RGB</quote> na Wikipediji</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid "&HTML; Hexadecimal Code"
msgstr "&HTML; Šestnajstiška koda"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may enter the &HTML; hexadecimal code representing the color in the "
"lower-right corner of the screen. For more information on this, see <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_colors\">the <quote>Web colors</"
"quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko &HTML; šestnajstiško kodo, ki predstavlja barvo v spodnjem "
"desnem kotu zaslona. Za več informacij o tem si oglejte <ulink url=\"https://"
"sl.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spletna_barva\">članek <quote>Spletna barva</quote> na "
"Wikipediji</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This value is also updated when selecting a color by other methods, so it "
"always accurately represents the currently selected color."
msgstr ""
"Ta vrednost se posodobi tudi pri izbiri barve z drugimi metodami, tako da "
"vedno natančno predstavlja trenutno izbrano barvo."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Colors"
msgstr "Barve po meri"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting a color, you may add it to the Custom Colors group so you "
"can use it later. To do so, click the <guibutton>Add to Custom Colors</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete barvo, jo lahko dodate v skupino Barve po meri, da jo lahko "
"uporabite pozneje. To storite tako, da kliknete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj barvam "
"po meri</guibutton>."
